snippet.title: Salvagette - turn-based bullet-hell class warfare!
snippet.description:
July 2021, PC, Web, iOS and Android

An updated and enhanced version of "Salvage", featuring new enemies, upgrades, secret endings, soundtrack and more!

Find out more https://e1sif.itch.io/salvagette
